  <text x="40" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Global Account Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">100만원 계좌 = 100억원 계좌</text>
  <text x="40" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">둘 다 '1표'로 집계</text>
  <text x="40" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">→ 군중 심리를 재는 도구</text>
  <rect x="370" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="390" y="100" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">돈을 센다 (명목가치)</text>
  <text x="390" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">펀딩비 · 미결제약정</text>
  <text x="390" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Notional-weighted</text>
  <text x="390" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">포지션 크기 × 가격으로</text>
  <text x="390" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">정산·집계</text>
  <text x="390" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">→ 청산 리스크를 재는 도구</text>
  <text x="20" y="278" fill="#fafafa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">예: 소액 롱 10계좌 vs 대형 숏 1계좌</text>
  <rect x="20" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#27191b"/>
  <text x="40" y="320" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">계좌 기준 → 10:1, 롱 압도적 우위</text>
  <rect x="370" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#182234"/>
  <text x="390" y="320" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">자본 기준 → 순숏 우위 가능</text>
  <text x="350" y="378" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">어긋남은 오류가 아니라, 서로 다른 질문에 대한 서로 다른 답이다</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="en">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">The Three Metrics Measure Different Units</text>
  <text x="20" y="52" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Same market, different questions</text>
  <rect x="20" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="40" y="100" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Counts people (accounts)</text>
  <text x="40" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Long/Short Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Global Account Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">A $700 account = a $7M account</text>
  <text x="40" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Both count as one "vote"</text>
  <text x="40" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">→ A crowd-sentiment tool</text>
  <rect x="370" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="390" y="100" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Counts money (notional)</text>
  <text x="390" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Funding Rate · Open Interest</text>
  <text x="390" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Notional-weighted</text>
  <text x="390" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Settled by position size</text>
  <text x="390" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">times price</text>
  <text x="390" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">→ A liquidation-risk tool</text>
  <text x="20" y="278" fill="#fafafa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Ex: 10 small long accounts vs 1 large short account</text>
  <rect x="20" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#27191b"/>
  <text x="40" y="320" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">By account &#8594; 10:1, heavily long</text>
  <rect x="370" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#182234"/>
  <text x="390" y="320" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">By capital &#8594; could be net short</text>
  <text x="350" y="378" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">The mismatch isn't an error — it's two answers to two different questions</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="ja">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
